reviewText: Interviews from 2015. Daughter enjoyed it anyway.
A Christmas gift for my daughter.  She loves it.
No Come with a concert DVD Amazon
No Music. All talk. Don't waste your money on this DVD. !!!!!!!!!!

My daughter was so excited to get this for Christmas but was highly disappointed when she played it for the first time only to see that all this DVD includes are interviews of the girls. Sad this is about a singing group and there's no music. Don't waste your money even if it is less than $10.
